      "startTime": 8.9668026527
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "speakerNameEn": "Everyone",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "TRINITYAiLEです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "TRINITYAiLE!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.9668026527,
      "endTime": 10.4313605388,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 10.708458209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "新春を飾る今日限りの特別な番組！\n私達トリエルがMCとして、生放送でお届けします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A special New Year’s program—only for today!\nWe‚ TRINITYAiLE‚ will be your MCs and bring it to you live!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.708458209,
      "endTime": 18.6427661898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 14.2644218842
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 18.8494328183
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "番組終了後には視聴者投票も実施！\n一位の挑戦者にはなんと！　ハワイ旅行をプレゼント！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After the show‚ we’ll also have a viewer vote!\nAnd the challenger who wins the first place will get—a trip to Hawaii!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.8494328183,
      "endTime": 27.574512164,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 27.7678452493
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、ぜひ投票よろしくお願いしま～す！\nではまず最初の挑戦企画です！　VTR……どうぞ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ please be sure to vote~!\nNow‚ let’s start with our first challenge! VTR… roll!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.7678452493,
      "endTime": 37.5366887094,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11168.843269400004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 38.670021852
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "……という訳で、さっそく最初の挑戦でした！\nめっちゃ盛り上がっとったなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…And that was our very first challenge!\nIt really got fired up‚ didn’t it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7366885187,
      "endTime": 46.6607009889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 41.4879733044
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 46.8607008936
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "見てるこっちもハラハラドキドキだったよね！\nハラハラドキドキと言えば……次の挑戦は……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Watching it had my heart pounding too!\nSpeaking of heart-pounding… the next challenge is…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8607008936,
      "endTime": 55.2630139353,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 55.4763472877
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "……はい！　私、天動瑠依の挑戦です！\n挑戦するのは……『トリエルに翼を授けよう』です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes! It’s my challenge—Rui Tendo’s!\nAnd my challenge is… “Let’s Give Wings to TRINITYAiLE”!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.4763472877,
      "endTime": 64.8740798316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 65.0607463839
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "おお！　トリエルに、翼……！？\nユニット名のAiLEにちなんでるんだね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oooh! Wings… to TRINITYAiLE!?\nSince our unit name is AiLE—“wing‚” right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.0607463839,
      "endTime": 71.56251525900001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 71.7625151636
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "要するに、瑠依ちゃんが本物の天使になる挑戦なん？\nあかん……ただでさえもうすでに天使やのに！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So basically‚ Rui-chan is trying to become a real angel?\nOh no… she’s already an angel as it is!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.7625151636,
      "endTime": 81.3314951898,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 81.5314949991
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "優？　もしかして茶化してる？\n今回の挑戦は、さらにもっと大規模なものなの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yu? Are you teasing me right now?\nThis challenge is on an even bigger scale than that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.5314949991,
      "endTime": 89.30006666189999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 89.5000665666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "生放送で挑戦するのをみなさんに見てもらうのは\n凄くドキドキしますが……絶対にやり遂げてみせます!",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Having everyone watch me attempt this live\nmakes me really nervous… but I’ll definitely see it through!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.5000665666,
      "endTime": 97.4608603479,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_cdstage-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "cdstage-01-noon",
      "startTime": 97.6475270909
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ瑠依ちゃんは、準備と移動がありますので\nみなさんはVTRをご覧になってお待ち下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then Rui-chan will need time to prepare and move to the location‚\nso everyone‚ please enjoy the VTR while you wait!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.6475270909,
      "endTime": 105.15943161679999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8905.2378019
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "――翼が、ほしい\nどこまでも高みへ羽ばたいていける、翼が――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—I want wings.\nWings that can soar endlessly into the heights—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.3527648928,
      "endTime": 113.22541818639999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.4820849103
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "最初にお話をいただいた時、真っ先に抱いたのは\nやってみたいっていう気持ちでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I first received the offer‚ the first thing I felt was—\nI really wanted to try it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.5320849103,
      "endTime": 121.8144657773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 122.0277989389
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "私……いえ、私達トリエルにとって\n『翼』はとても重要なファクターですから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For me… no‚ for all of us in TRINITYAiLE—\n“Wings” are a very important factor for us…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.0277989389,
      "endTime": 130.1689554217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 130.35562226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんの挑戦……\nその準備は、十月から始まっていました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan’s challenge…\nThe preparations for it actually began back in October.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.35562226,
      "endTime": 135.81795765569998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "全国のトリエルファンが集まって\n瑠依ちゃんを応援したい一心で作った物",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The thing TRINITYAiLE fans from all over the country made‚\nand poured their hearts into to support Rui-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.0313000681,
      "endTime": 144.11252479569998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "それが、翼――\nとても大きな、グライダー……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's… the wings—\nA huge glider!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.3258582434,
      "endTime": 149.755336698,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6816.145197600008
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-rui010.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみんなが用意してくれたこの翼を背負って\nどこまで空を翔けることが出来るのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With these wings that all our fans made for me—\nHow far I’ll be able to fly through the sky…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.942003441,
      "endTime": 158.0602574351,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2501_01_02-rui011.m4a",
