      "text": "（毎日相談したり練習を繰り返してきたんだもの）\n（その努力を、私は裏切りたくない）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（We discussed and practiced every single day.）\n（I won’t betray all that effort.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 372.7587151211,
      "endTime": 380.3159711522,
      "sfxList": []
